{"tid":1475444,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我個新移民同事問我有冇玩抖音，我答完後比全場同事笑","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:06:33.000Z","uid":154872,"like":27,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e649152e9820ea665cfb04eb02524a384699b2aa","tid":1475444,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"話說我條team最近請左個新移民大陸妹<br />\n<br />\n都好後生，個樣都ok的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚team dinner佢坐我隔離，<br />\n<br />\n我地傾緊IG po左啲咩<br />\n<br />\n咁佢突然插嘴話有冇人玩抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場啲同事（包括我）都冇玩的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我為左表現前輩嘅風範，唯有扮識<br />\n<br />\n我以為抖陰（下陰？）係啲不文野（fing一fing下邊咁）<br />\n<br />\n咁就企起身fing一fing下身打算助下興<br />\n<br />\n點知做完我笑笑口坐低，但全場靜左<br />\n<br />\n然後比個女同事打左我一巴話我低俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到去佢仲想屈我言語性騷擾要我比20萬佢<br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef77293ca3806b957bad71ac167020fd26652a0","tid":1475444,"uid":17799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e649152e9820ea665cfb04eb02524a384699b2aa","tid":1475444,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"話說我條team最近請左個新移民大陸妹<br />\n<br />\n都好後生，個樣都ok的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚team dinner佢坐我隔離，<br />\n<br />\n我地傾緊IG po左啲咩<br />\n<br />\n咁佢突然插嘴話有冇人玩抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場啲同事（包括我）都冇玩的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我為左表現前輩嘅風範，唯有扮識<br />\n<br />\n我以為抖陰（下陰？）係啲不